{"per_page":10,"total":5,"current":4,"data":[{"title":"MarkDown使用","date":"2018-12-15T21:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年12月15日","L":"2018/12/15","MM-DD":"12-15"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>Markdown是约翰·格鲁伯发明的轻量级标记语言，方便用易读易写的纯文本格式编写文档，然后转换成有效的XHTML（或者HTML）。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2018/12/15/MarkdownLangure","categories":["Fun"]},{"title":"iOS-组件化","date":"2018-11-22T21:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年11月22日","L":"2018/11/22","MM-DD":"11-22"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>当项目越来越复杂的时候，平时的通用方案就不太实用了，这个时候就需要对项目组件化了。 组件化这个东西其实并不复杂，本质上是一种app架构思路。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2018/11/22/IOS_ComponentBased","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"iOS内存管理与多线程","date":"2018-11-08T21:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年11月8日","L":"2018/11/08","MM-DD":"11-08"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>在iOS中我们如何进行内存管理</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2018/11/08/OC_HighLevel_Progamming","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"UITxtView跟随KeyBoard弹起收回","date":"2018-11-01T21:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年11月1日","L":"2018/11/01","MM-DD":"11-01"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>iOS开发中，经常需求点击输入框后，键盘弹起，而输入框也会出现在键盘上方，以UITxtView为例来实现。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2018/11/01/UITextViewMakeKeyboardView","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"iOS-剖析UIView","date":"2018-10-30T21:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年10月30日","L":"2018/10/30","MM-DD":"10-30"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>UIView在iOS中则是在屏幕上用来管理一块矩形区域的对象，也是iOS开发中最为基础的UI控件。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2018/10/30/IOS_UIview","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"App 上架流程","date":"2018-09-01T21:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年9月1日","L":"2018/09/01","MM-DD":"09-01"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>App 的 上架 和 真机测试，算是App开发流程的最后一步了，那么苹果是如何保证 App Store 上 App 的安全性，以及本地真机测试时苹果是如何授权的呢？</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2018/09/01/AppAddAppStore","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"Apple Push Notification service","date":"2018-07-30T21:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年7月30日","L":"2018/07/30","MM-DD":"07-30"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>APNs : Apple Push Notification service 的简称，由苹果公司提供的推送通知服务</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2018/07/30/ApplePushNotification","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"色彩笔记","date":"2018-04-12T21:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年4月12日","L":"2018/04/12","MM-DD":"04-12"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>在计算机中，计算机本身并不能直接通过名字识别色彩，而是通过数字完成记录的。<br>\n<img src=\"https://image.boxueio.com/color-basics-2@2x.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2018/04/12/Color_Notes","categories":["Fun","UI"]},{"title":"2017年的回顾","date":"2017-12-29T21:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2017年12月29日","L":"2017/12/29","MM-DD":"12-29"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>2017年，我经历了什么？</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2017/12/29/2017-Annual-Summary","categories":["Dailylife"]},{"title":"Bit-Computing","date":"2017-12-18T21:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2017年12月18日","L":"2017/12/18","MM-DD":"12-18"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>位运算是对内存中的数据(二进制数据)直接进行二进制运算操作</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2017/12/18/Bit-Computing","categories":["ComputerScience","位运算"]}]}